{"tid":1365574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[勇武定和理非] 不如一齊停一停 諗一諗?","createTime":"2019-07-25T16:26:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T05:01:10.000Z","uid":16376,"like":55,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ae30d6216d779f4710d2360e6fe5281dfe2a6335","tid":1365574,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:26:13.000Z","msg":"我地發夢試過和理非, 又試過勇武<br />\n我地堅持左個幾月, 每個星期都發過夢<br />\n大家一齊付出過, 一齊努力過<br />\n而對家係721元朗事件爆左單柒野 (我相信咁落去一定會爆更多柒野)<br />\n不如趁機停一停, 諗一諗<br />\n係咪真係要發夢個陣勇武入元朗<br />\n不如趁對家自己柒左, 大家做返一次和理非 <br />\n再拉攏更多中間派, 甚至可以令到有公務員罷工 (因為721事件後, 令到有大量公務員都響應左運動)<br />\n而家777既籌碼就係有班公務員為佢做野<br />\n但如果佢地都反抗政府, 我地勝算亦在望<br />\n又可以宣揚警黑一家親呢個訊息俾外國知, 落中共面<br />\n<br />\n不如大家真係停一停 諗一諗 大家跟著既行動以咩方向為主, 用咩方法抗爭！<br />\n都係個句, 我地兄弟爬山各自努力, 目標都係一樣, 亦會尊重大家意見<br />\n非分化非割席, 只係想大家趁對面爆左單柒野, 大家可以冷靜諗一諗。"},{"pid":"09b17a887e4bbbd801e5bed2b9375d7df436eaf8","tid":1365574,"uid":34047,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:27:41.000Z","msg":"用反黑反恐做主題<br />\n搶道德高地<br />\n唔比位人入<br />\n挾埋班中立既<br />\n和理非回合"},{"pid":"b05bddafa0d3902802bf1bb7caaa6f5ef604bb73","tid":1365574,"uid":283266,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:28:06.000Z","msg":"我地絕對唔會係主動嗰邊，但如果對家打到埋嚟，一定要還手。"},{"pid":"840b3ec84b154fa9693d91277a4c03b165c29f4a","tid":1365574,"uid":34047,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"09b17a887e4bbbd801e5bed2b9375d7df436eaf8","tid":1365574,"uid":34047,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:27:41.000Z","msg":"用反黑反恐做主題<br />\n搶道德高地<br />\n唔比位人入<br />\n挾埋班中立既<br />\n和理非回合"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:28:52.000Z","msg":"當然 如果人地郁手既<br />\n就代表對方係支持恐怖襲擊<br />\n當然要以武制暴"},{"pid":"ab79b38ebbbf35a421d19b32c7a24900337eb865","tid":1365574,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09b17a887e4bbbd801e5bed2b9375d7df436eaf8","tid":1365574,"uid":34047,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:27:41.000Z","msg":"用反黑反恐做主題<br />\n搶道德高地<br />\n唔比位人入<br />\n挾埋班中立既<br />\n和理非回合"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:29:41.000Z","msg":"係  今次都係因為對家踩左道德底線<br />\n令好多唔出聲既人都出聲<br />\n同埋公務員都響應左<br />\n不如借機就發大 警黑一家親"},{"pid":"94f2e3a21abac599d607e71bb9e710c9a7f5007d","tid":1365574,"uid":16376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"840b3ec84b154fa9693d91277a4c03b165c29f4a","tid":1365574,"uid":34047,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"09b17a887e4bbbd801e5bed2b9375d7df436eaf8","tid":1365574,"uid":34047,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:27:41.000Z","msg":"用反黑反恐做主題<br />\n搶道德高地<br />\n唔比位人入<br />\n挾埋班中立既<br />\n和理非回合"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:28:52.000Z","msg":"當然 如果人地郁手既<br />\n就代表對方係支持恐怖襲擊<br />\n當然要以武制暴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:31:43.000Z","msg":"相信發夢個日 世界各地好多傳媒都黎<br />\n如果對家郁手, 大家都會影曬, 而當市民受到人生安危, 係可以自衛<br />\n如果警察係夢境入面唔做野, 又可以俾全世界知香港既7野"},{"pid":"248419e1b82310504e0358760fee84576acb986c","tid":1365574,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:33:31.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n俾更多人討論"},{"pid":"abe5b22fffb6fd55e1207f07c455511f955b5fa4","tid":1365574,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:33:59.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n俾更多人討論"},{"pid":"1ca71df196d1a1a3bd09fa10cc997f9d785c92bc","tid":1365574,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:34:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/F2dYoLwLqv8?t=9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF2dYoLwLqv8%3Ft%3D9&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hJnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=3b6b0aa6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/F2dYoLwLqv8?t=9</a>"},{"pid":"50e4836bf06ff9edf0d2f35cf7ffa7bf9d4235a4","tid":1365574,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ca71df196d1a1a3bd09fa10cc997f9d785c92bc","tid":1365574,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:34:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/F2dYoLwLqv8?t=9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF2dYoLwLqv8%3Ft%3D9&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hJnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=3b6b0aa6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/F2dYoLwLqv8?t=9</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:36:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746e20fce7cc5b07510a8af93a2c9498ce5c0273","tid":1365574,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:36:23.000Z","msg":"推俾更多人討論"},{"pid":"b78bd00b6e7f57100c432daf141e21e605b19a93","tid":1365574,"uid":271857,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:37:01.000Z","msg":"大家可能仲未認清形勢。<br />\n政府已無賴到呢個地步，有咩做唔出?<br />\n真係可以下星期人大宣布一國一制拉哂去勞改<br />\n而香港人係無任何反駁餘地。<br />\n調查? 輿論? 已經全部失效<br />\n西方都表態唔理住，你還可做什麼?<br />\n真係同佢駁命咩? 咪傻啦。<br />\n時不與我，返去轁光養悔<br />\n搵啲娛樂舒援下情緒<br />\n事急則緩，事緩則圓。來日方長。<br />\n用選票來決定區議會和立法會。<br />\n再聰明既人都要能屈能伸<br />\n司馬懿都要轁光養晦數十年先成大業。<br />\n獅子王受挫敗也要去第二度避開下<br />\nhakuna matata<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nbY_aP-alkw&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=184\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnbY_aP-alkw%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%26t%3D184&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hJnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=8183ceb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nbY_aP-alkw&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=184</a>"},{"pid":"a8251724e1f064ccef438ea1d85bce181bb54cdb","tid":1365574,"uid":259302,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:37:18.000Z","msg":"<strong>7.27入元朗踩場</strong><br />\n點樣先係將踩場發揮到<strong>極緻</strong>？就係入到人地頭，佢最想發生嘅事發生唔到，最唔想發生嘅事發生左。<br />\n<br />\n元朗啲黑社會最想就係打鳩啲黑衫示威者，要黑衫示威者打直入打橫出。對佢地最大嘅侮辱就係幾萬個黑衫示威者入去元朗佢地地頭周圍行，跟住咩事都無敢行返去元朗。<br />\n<br />\n同佢地打，我地實有人傷，正正係佢地想發生嘅事&mdash;&mdash;黑衫示威者入得元朗就無得預咩事都無敢返出去。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>我地幾萬人着黑衫入元朗，完膚無傷敢行返出元朗，就係對元朗黑社會最大嘅嘲諷。</strong>"},{"pid":"01d5dff82049049afeb33385193abd2b3ed92275","tid":1365574,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8251724e1f064ccef438ea1d85bce181bb54cdb","tid":1365574,"uid":259302,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:37:18.000Z","msg":"<strong>7.27入元朗踩場</strong><br />\n點樣先係將踩場發揮到<strong>極緻</strong>？就係入到人地頭，佢最想發生嘅事發生唔到，最唔想發生嘅事發生左。<br />\n<br />\n元朗啲黑社會最想就係打鳩啲黑衫示威者，要黑衫示威者打直入打橫出。對佢地最大嘅侮辱就係幾萬個黑衫示威者入去元朗佢地地頭周圍行，跟住咩事都無敢行返去元朗。<br />\n<br />\n同佢地打，我地實有人傷，正正係佢地想發生嘅事&mdash;&mdash;黑衫示威者入得元朗就無得預咩事都無敢返出去。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>我地幾萬人着黑衫入元朗，完膚無傷敢行返出元朗，就係對元朗黑社會最大嘅嘲諷。</strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:38:12.000Z","msg":"的確係!<br />\n我地幾多個人入去, 就幾多個人出黎"},{"pid":"85d2a8e4657dcf67642b0d267a948f022927b6f0","tid":1365574,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b78bd00b6e7f57100c432daf141e21e605b19a93","tid":1365574,"uid":271857,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:37:01.000Z","msg":"大家可能仲未認清形勢。<br />\n政府已無賴到呢個地步，有咩做唔出?<br />\n真係可以下星期人大宣布一國一制拉哂去勞改<br />\n而香港人係無任何反駁餘地。<br />\n調查? 輿論? 已經全部失效<br />\n西方都表態唔理住，你還可做什麼?<br />\n真係同佢駁命咩? 咪傻啦。<br />\n時不與我，返去轁光養悔<br />\n搵啲娛樂舒援下情緒<br />\n事急則緩，事緩則圓。來日方長。<br />\n用選票來決定區議會和立法會。<br />\n再聰明既人都要能屈能伸<br />\n司馬懿都要轁光養晦數十年先成大業。<br />\n獅子王受挫敗也要去第二度避開下<br />\nhakuna matata<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nbY_aP-alkw&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=184\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnbY_aP-alkw%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%26t%3D184&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hJnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=8183ceb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nbY_aP-alkw&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=184</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:38:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s